# Lambda deployment zip

After **any** edit under `lambda/admin-auth/` (including `index.mjs` or `package.json`), run from the **repository root**:

```bash
npm run package:lambda
```

This produces **`dist/lambda-admin-auth.zip`** for upload to AWS Lambda. Do not skip this step when handing off deployable artifacts.

If `scripts/package-lambda.mjs` changes, run the same command so packaging stays verified.
